  }, "v22"), mdx("p", null, "V\xEC c\u1EDB ch\xFAng, t\u1EA5t c\u1EA3 c\xE1c t\xF9 binh Giu-\u0111a \u1EDF Ba-by-l\xF4n s\u1EBD d\xF9ng l\u1EDDi nguy\u1EC1n r\u1EE7a n\u1EA7y: 'Nguy\u1EC7n CH\xDAA \u0111\u1ED1i x\u1EED v\u1EDBi ng\u01B0\u01A1i nh\u01B0 X\xEA-\u0111\xEA-kia v\xE0 A-h\xE1p, m\xE0 vua Ba-by-l\xF4n \u0111\xE3 h\u1ECFa thi\xEAu.' "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v23"
  }, "v23"), mdx("p", null, "Ch\xFAng \u0111\xE3 l\xE0m nhi\u1EC1u \u0111i\u1EC1u \xE1c trong v\xF2ng d\xE2n \xCDt-ra-en, ch\xFAng \u0111\xE3 ph\u1EA1m t\u1ED9i t\xE0 d\xE2m v\u1EDBi v\u1EE3 c\u1EE7a l\xE1ng gi\u1EC1ng m\xECnh. Ch\xFAng \u0111\xE3 n\xF3i d\u1ED1i v\xE0 b\u1EA3o r\u1EB1ng nh\u1EEFng l\u1EDDi \u0111\xF3 \u0111\u1EBFn t\u1EEB ta. Ta kh\xF4ng h\u1EC1 b\u1EA3o ch\xFAng l\xE0m nh\u01B0 th\u1EBF. Ta bi\u1EBFt ch\xFAng l\xE0m \u0111i\u1EC1u g\xEC; ta l\xE0m ch\u1EE9ng cho vi\u1EC7c \u0111\xF3,\" CH\xDAA ph\xE1n v\u1EADy.S\u1EE9 \u0111i\u1EC7p c\u1EE7a Th\u01B0\u1EE3ng \u0110\u1EBF cho S\xEA-mai-gia "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v24"
  }, "v24"), mdx("p", null, "Ngo\xE0i ra c\u0169ng b\u1EA3o v\u1EDBi S\xEA-mai-gia, thu\u1ED9c gia \u0111\xECnh N\xEA-h\xEA-lam nh\u01B0 sau. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v25"
  }, "v25"), mdx("p", null, "CH\xDAA To\xE0n N\u0103ng, Th\u01B0\u1EE3ng \u0110\u1EBF c\u1EE7a \xCDt-ra-en ph\xE1n: \"H\u1EE1i S\xEA-mai-gia, ng\u01B0\u01A1i nh\xE2n danh m\xECnh g\u1EDFi th\u01B0 cho to\xE0n d\xE2n c\u01B0 Gi\xEA-ru-sa-lem, cho th\u1EA7y t\u1EBF l\u1EC5 X\xF4-ph\xF4-ni, con Ma-a-s\xEA-gia, c\xF9ng t\u1EA5t c\u1EA3 c\xE1c th\u1EA7y t\u1EBF l\u1EC5. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v26"
