    "id": "v27"
  }, "v27"), mdx("p", null, "C\xF2n Gi\xEA-r\xEA-mi ng\u01B0\u1EDDi A-na-th\u1ED1t h\xE0nh \u0111\u1ED9ng nh\u01B0 nh\xE0 ti\xEAn tri sao ng\u01B0\u01A1i kh\xF4ng b\u1EAFt? "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v28"
  }, "v28"), mdx("p", null, "Gi\xEA-r\xEA-mi \u0111\xE3 g\u1EDFi th\u01B0 sau \u0111\xE2y cho ch\xFAng ta \u1EDF Ba-by-l\xF4n: C\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i s\u1EBD ph\u1EA3i \u1EDF \u0111\xF3 r\u1EA5t l\xE2u cho n\xEAn h\xE3y x\xE2y nh\xE0 v\xE0 l\u1EADp nghi\u1EC7p \u0111i. H\xE3y tr\u1ED3ng v\u01B0\u1EDDn t\u01B0\u1EE3c v\xE0 \u0103n hoa qu\u1EA3 c\u1EE7a ch\xFAng.'\" "), mdx("h6", {
