  }, "v29"), mdx("p", null, "Th\u1EA7y t\u1EBF l\u1EC5 X\xF4-ph\xF4-ni \u0111\u1ECDc th\u01B0 cho nh\xE0 ti\xEAn tri Gi\xEA-r\xEA-mi. "), mdx("h6", {
